description: Destination Desserts is a purpose driven bakery, formed with two guiding principles…A social venture designed to train, employ and advance the lives of people with head injuries and other cognitive learning conditions. The other is to grow an exciting business that passionately bakes sinfully good cookies, cupcakes and other mouth-watering creations with a social responsibility. 100% of our proceeds go to support the nationally recognized Center For Head Injury Services.
name: Destination Desserts
